In [8]:
# filling null values
for i in df.columns:
    if df[i].dtypes==object:
        df[i]=df[i].fillna(df[i].mode()[0])
    else:
        df[i]=df[i].fillna(df[i].mean())

# visualising relation and patterns with price column by scatterplot
from matplotlib.pyplot import show
for i in df.columns:
    sns.scatterplot(data=df,x=i,y='Price')
    print('Price vs ',i)
    show()
